| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0574 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: ed2d1261-feaa-5f57-ba1f-3023fb98a61b"
